title: Valiant Comics COMPLETE May 2012 through July 2015
description:
This torrent contains every single comic published by Valiant Entertainment from the Summer of Valiant 2012 through to July 29th 2015. 

It does NOT contain Book of Death: Legends of the Geomancer #01, as that's the one title I haven't been able to find, nor will it ever be issued digitally or published in an omnibus. Ever. I wasn't even able to find it at my LCS.

Thanks to all the uploaders and scanners out there. Thanks also to all the incredibly talented writers, artists, and the publisher, for working on these amazing books. Buy them when you can, please.

note: the X-O 25th Anniversary special was published between #036 and #037.

Enjoy, and seed!
